Since its launch in 2009 kiwilimón has revolutionized the way home cooks connect with each other through their own recipes offering their community dynamic content and becoming the leading cooking channel for advertisers. Kiwilimón currently has over half a million registered loyal users and over 13,000 cooking recipes.

Kiwilimón also has one of the most successful cooking apps in Spanish that has reached over 300,000 downloads since their launch in 2013. It has been named one of Google's top apps of 2015 in Mexico and is also available in the apple store.
